## 4. The "Builder’s Blueprint" (Product Strategy)

| Feature | The Vibe-Coded MVP | The Enterprise Solution |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Data Input** | Manual CSV upload of SKU prices. | Real-time ERP/POS integration. |
| **Benchmark** | National BLS Category Average. | Hyper-local, competitor-specific indices. |
| **Analysis** | Historical Price vs. Inflation Gap. | Predictive "What-If" revenue modeling. |
| **Output** | Visual "Margin Alert" Dashboard. | Automated price updates sent to ESL (Electronic Shelf Labels). |

### Minimum Viable Logic (MVL)
The **"Inflation-to-Price Delta."** If $CPI\ Growth > Price\ Growth$, show a **Red Alert**. This single calculation provides immediate, actionable business value by identifying which products are losing money in real terms.

